1.title: «Novia y viuda»
1.plot: About to be captured by the police in 2007, Sara recalls a joyful day in Tijuana that turned tragic, forever changing the direction of her life.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Vicente's sister-in-law, Mariana, realizes she has a target on her back. Sara learns her husband was involved in shady dealings.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: When Felipe accuses him of an impropriety, Junio loses his temper and, later, pays the consequences. Sara finds herself living in a car.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Junio gets bad news from the doctor. To save his skin, Felipe makes a deal with El Indio. Mariana is offered a position of power, with one condition.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Sara comes face to face with El Capi. Realizing the hospital surgeon is in cahoots with El Indio, Junio forces him to confess what he did to Sara.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: In Guadalajara, Salvador falls ill. Meanwhile, the boss of new neighbor Aracely must contend with a medical emergency of her own at her beauty salon.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: The doctor gives Sara grave news. Mariana tells El Indio that Junio is now a threat. Thinking the undercover cop is following her, Sara makes a scene.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: Mariana lures Junio into an ambush. Sara realizes where the $3 million is hidden. Salvador regains consciousness and shares vital information.

9.title: Episode #1.9
9.plot: Sara gets a surprise gift. To save herself, Mariana tells a secret to Junio. The sisters' bodies are found. Aracely recognizes a suspect on a flier.

10.title: Episode #1.10
10.plot: Miriam finds a record of Magdalena's procedure. Sara makes her way to Mexicali, unaware she's being followed. Elio recognizes one of the bodies.

11.title: Episode #1.11
11.plot: Juan ensures Miriam will keep quiet. Pretending to be a forensic doctor, Elio visits Lupita. A vengeful Berta gets a gun and tracks down Sara.

12.title: Episode #1.12
12.plot: Enriqueta picks a person to pin her crimes on. Junio plots a way to get Sara past police checkpoints. Josefina learns Berta's prognosis.

13.title: Episode #1.13
13.plot: Elio arrives at the salon with a search warrant. Carlota gets a horrifying voicemail. Threatened with bodily harm, Aracely scrambles to pay her debt.

14.title: Episode #1.14
14.plot: Sara makes an ally in jail. To lure Felipe, Elio feeds false information to Gutierrez. Aracely returns to old vices. Enriqueta plans a career change.

15.title: Episode #1.15
15.plot: Felipe and Mariana follow Sara home, where Junio proves himself a hero. During a bust, Elio suspects police corruption. Sara learns of Miriam's past.

16.title: Episode #1.16
16.plot: Lupita begs Enriqueta to perform breast implant surgery on her. Salvador develops a complication. Juan plots with Miriam's ex. Empanada returns.

17.title: Episode #1.17
17.plot: Elio learns who is in cahoots with Cortés, and later faces an ethical dilemma. While Lupita goes under the knife, her blood test results come back.

18.title: Episode #1.18
18.plot: Aracely succumbs to temptation to forget her woes. Sara unleashes her anger on Enriqueta, who gets revenge. Juan manipulates Miriam to get her son.

19.title: Episode #1.19
19.plot: Enriqueta finds herself in a new home but without allies. Sara and Elio's relationship reaches a turning point. The police receive a disturbing video.

20.title: Episode #1.20
20.plot: Mariana goes to Colombia. Aracely runs into an ex. Elio is backed into a corner at work. Enriqueta finds a way to regain the upper hand with Cornelia.

21.title: Episode #1.21
21.plot: Aracely gets a frantic call from her mother. Carlota tries to reconcile with Sara. Mariana overhears Juan on the phone. Sara discovers Elio's stash.

22.title: Episode #1.22
22.plot: Juan launches his kidnapping plan. At Salvador's new hospital, Sara gets some crushing news and later discovers that Elio's been keeping a secret.

23.title: Episode #1.23
23.plot: Carlota gets some good news. Enriqueta's assassin starts her mission. Elio's domestic troubles come to light. Aracely is reunited with Plutarco.

24.title: Episode #1.24
24.plot: When Salvador's need for a transplant becomes urgent, Elio uses insider information to intercept a shipment of drug money and pay for the surgery.

25.title: Episode #1.25
25.plot: Berta thwarts Carlota's plans to donate her kidney. Pepito is lured away from school. Elio tries to sell what he stole. Vanessa recalls a tragic day.

26.title: Episode #1.26
26.plot: Berta abuses her power as mayor. Sara begs Elio to get her in a meeting with Quintanilla. Vanessa snoops around the hospital for information.

27.title: Episode #1.27
27.plot: Sara strikes a deal with Quintanilla, but with strings attached. Vanessa's tampering with Patricia's food and drink results in an emergency.

28.title: Episode #1.28
28.plot: Salvador undergoes the transplant procedure. Arnulfo gets Pepito's DNA test results. Elio pays his debt to El Indio and gets an unexpected response.

29.title: Episode #1.29
29.plot: Pepito is groomed for a future career. Sara gets two surprise gifts. Miriam gives Sara smuggling tips. Elio has a delicate talk with Patricia.

30.title: Episode #1.30
30.plot: Vanessa gets revenge against Elio. Sara does her first smuggling job. Juan gets out of prison. Arnulfo and Empanada feed Pepito a lie about his mom.

31.title: Episode #1.31
31.plot: Vanessa's father reveals a secret to Elio. Quintanilla asks to see Sara right away. Juan seeks Enriqueta's help. Sara gets a reward she doesn't want.

32.title: Episode #1.32
32.plot: Juan confronts Empanada for betraying him. Sara comes clean to Elio about her new job, and later gets news that leads her to choose a path of revenge.

33.title: Episode #1.33
33.plot: Juan plants an explosive device. Empanada hires someone to kill Enriqueta in prison. Vanessa confronts Elio at gunpoint, with tragic consequences.

34.title: Episode #1.34
34.plot: Enriqueta's former ally in prison turns against her. Quintanilla leaves a message for El Indio on Sara's behalf. Elio learns who planted the bomb.

35.title: Episode #1.35
35.plot: Aracely introduces Plutarco to her family. Vanessa's father grants Elio a secret favor. Sara helps Quintanilla salvage a blocked drug shipment.

36.title: Episode #1.36
36.plot: Aracely's ex blackmails her. El Indio discovers fate has already avenged his son's death. Elio is blindsided in prison. Pepito tries to run away.

37.title: Episode #1.37
37.plot: Empanada tries to seduce Mariana. Martín ruins Aracely and Plutarco's romantic evening. While in Los Angeles, Sara spots Arnulfo and confronts him.

38.title: Episode #1.38
38.plot: Sara reveals a happy secret to an inconsolable Aracely. While trying to smuggle Quintanilla's $70 million, Elio and Sara are stopped at the border.

39.title: Episode #1.39
39.plot: Three years pass. Sara decides she will retire from smuggling and laundering after completing one last job, her biggest and riskiest one yet.

40.title: Episode #1.40
40.plot: While smuggling the $150 million, Sara is stopped at the border. Salvador no longer believes his mother's promises. Berta's maid drops a bombshell.

41.title: Episode #1.41
41.plot: Sara is forced to pay for Vicente's past. Rufino collects evidence of Empanada's true nature. Salvador breaks the rules and answers a phone call.

42.title: Episode #1.42
42.plot: Quintanilla cuts ties with Elio. Aracely reconnects with Plutarco. Carlota invites Berta to visit. Miriam and Joaquín prepare to cross the border.

43.title: Episode #1.43
43.plot: The Drug Enforcement Agency learns there's a price on Elio's head. Miriam and Joaquín reach the border. A plumbing problem leads to a discovery.

44.title: Episode #1.44
44.plot: Miriam finds her son. Edith goes undercover as Sara's new cellmate. Quintanilla plans to kill El Indio's secret boss. The DEA offers Sara a deal.

45.title: Episode #1.45
45.plot: Elio is shot by El Indio's hit man. Edith eavesdrops on Sara in a private conversation. Rufino spots Empanada with El Indio. Cruz attacks Visitación.

46.title: Episode #1.46
46.plot: Both cartels prepare for the cardinal's arrival in Guadalajara. Cortés takes down a fellow PGR officer. Sara and Edith enter into a partnership.

47.title: Episode #1.47
47.plot: Aracely is robbed of the $300,000, and later suffers another kind of loss. Elio puts a plan in motion to exonerate Sara. Josefina makes a grave error.

48.title: Episode #1.48
48.plot: Aracely's heartbreak is doubled. El Indio gives Empanada instructions for his mission. Elio pressures Sara to ask Quintanilla for one last job.

49.title: Episode #1.49
49.plot: El Teca asks Sara to meet him, but to come alone. Judge Creel calls Elio with a warning. Empanada embarks on his mission. Aracely confronts Martín.

50.title: Episode #1.50
50.plot: Martín provokes Aracely until she snaps. The DEA plants a bug in the salon. Sara gets devastating news. Plutarco makes a confession to Aracely.

51.title: Episode #1.51
51.plot: When Sara is accused of murder, she gets a new look and passport and goes on the run from the DEA and PGR. In a weak moment, Josefina calls Felipe.

52.title: Episode #1.52
52.plot: Sara narrowly escapes to L.A. but is soon found. Edith goes undercover again, this time getting a job at the salon. Josefina makes a sacrifice.

53.title: Episode #1.53
53.plot: Sara agrees to work for El Teca under one condition. Arnulfo forces Pepito to work as a debt collector. Martín plots against Aracely.

54.title: Episode #1.54
54.plot: Sara has trouble getting a meeting with Montero, but a stranger offers help. Aracely's uncle visits the salon, triggering painful memories.

55.title: Episode #1.55
55.plot: Sara meets with Montero. Miriam spots Arnulfo in Guadalajara and confronts him. While his father is away, Pepito tries to run away again.

56.title: Episode #1.56
56.plot: Miriam and Joaquín act on their feelings for each other. When Salvador falls ill, Sara defies El Teca's orders. Josefina's son is kidnapped.

57.title: Episode #1.57
57.plot: To help Josefina get her son back, Sara meets with Felipe. Manuel pays Sara a surprise visit. El Teca lays a deadly trap for Edith.

58.title: Episode #1.58
58.plot: El Teca reveals a lifelong obsession. Sara opens a new front and is given her first task. Plutarco demands to know the truth about Aracely's job.

59.title: Episode #1.59
59.plot: Plutarco reacts surprisingly to Aracely's confession. Cornelia proves untrustworthy. Felipe eliminates a threat. Sara and Quintanilla strike a deal.

60.title: Episode #1.60
60.plot: Aracely uses her expertise to ruin Felipe's campaign. Sara and Joaquín go to San Diego to rescue Pepito. Manuel finds a way to bond with Salvador.

61.title: Episode #1.61
61.plot: While watching the news, Plutarco recognizes Aracely in the video with Felipe. Quintanilla overhears Arnulfo and Tuercas plotting against Sara.

62.title: Episode #1.62
62.plot: Among the shootout's casualties is someone dear to Sara. Felipe takes extreme measures to ensure he's elected. Cornelia is caught red-handed.

63.title: Episode #1.63
63.plot: Cornelia shifts suspicion from herself and onto Sara. Manuel is more than he pretends to be. Sara asks Quintanilla to kill someone.

64.title: Episode #1.64
64.plot: As Sara visits Barba's brother with an offer, her smugglers make their way to the United States and Colombia. El Teca's tunnels hold a sad secret.

65.title: Episode #1.65
65.plot: Alicia endures a humiliating DEA interrogation. El Teca sends a warning to Cornelia. After giving El Teca an ultimatum, Sara is abducted by Felipe.

66.title: Episode #1.66
66.plot: Cornelia tells El Teca where the stolen money is hidden. The DEA gathers evidence to turn Sara against El Teca. Sara gets a troubling anonymous tip.

67.title: Episode #1.67
67.plot: Cornelia is forced to confess. Sara learns El Teca is still using kids as mules, and later spots Manuel with El Indio. Josefina gives Berta a gift.

68.title: Episode #1.68
68.plot: The DEA opens Sara's eyes to what's been happening behind her back. Berta accepts Sara's gift. Aracely preps Alicia to get revenge against the DEA.

69.title: Episode #1.69
69.plot: Alicia lures her prey. Aracely plans a questionable strategy to gather intel for Sara. Manuel realizes Sara is on to him. El Teca proposes to Sara.

70.title: Episode #1.70
70.plot: Aracely seduces El Indio. Sara replies to El Teca's proposal. A surprise move by Mexico's president upsets the lives of Sara and her family.

71.title: Episode #1.71
71.plot: Manuel finds Sara. When Miriam's torturers threaten to hurt Pepito, she spills. Plutarco learns what Aracely did with El Indio. Salvador is abducted.

72.title: Episode #1.72
72.plot: Sara is forced to role-play a twisted fantasy with El Teca while Manuel, Joaquín and Plutarco try to rescue her son from the warehouse.

73.title: Episode #1.73
73.plot: Manuel makes an unexpected move while he and Sara are on the run. El Teca pulls some strings. Sara unknowingly leaves a loose end behind.

1.title: Episode #2.1
1.plot: After five years of waiting in prison, Sara receives an unexpected sentence. El Teca tries to kidnap Sara, but captures someone close to her instead.

2.title: Episode #2.2
2.plot: At the airport, El Indio scrambles to cover the cartel's tracks. Consuelo makes a sacrifice, enabling Sara and Faría to immediately attempt an escape.

3.title: Episode #2.3
3.plot: El Teca gets a hint about the person who bribed the judge in Sara's sentencing. Sara finds herself stuck in close quarters with bully Makoki.

4.title: Episode #2.4
4.plot: At Mario's party, Aracely sees El Teca making a secret deal with a VIP. Sara is sent to the same hospital as her son. El Teca spots a familiar tattoo.

5.title: Episode #2.5
5.plot: Aracely is used as a pawn. El Teca tells Sara who was behind her sentence and offers his protection. Manuel plans an ambush.

6.title: Episode #2.6
6.plot: A meeting in Cali turns ugly for Quintanilla. Sara and Manuel attack El Teca's ranch. El Indio tries to force Aracely to reveal the photo's source.

7.title: Episode #2.7
7.plot: In a violent chase, Sara and Manuel must assume some risks. El Indio Amaro kills Plutarco.

8.title: Episode #2.8
8.plot: Pepito goes to his job interview. El Teca launches a full-scale attack, resulting in mass casualties. Quintanilla learns a family secret.

9.title: Episode #2.9
9.plot: Miriam makes a difficult choice. Salvador has a scary episode. Pepito comes to a stranger's rescue. Sara realizes what she must do to conquer El Teca.

10.title: Episode #2.10
10.plot: Peer pressure causes Pepito to make a poor choice. Sara's introduction to Mario leads to an important contact. Salvador wanders off and finds trouble.

11.title: Episode #2.11
11.plot: Sara tries to save her son from his hallucinations. Joaquín regains consciousness. The debt collectors' threats force Sara to play her last card.

12.title: Episode #2.12
12.plot: El Teca demands proof of Sara's loyalty to him. Erick convinces Manuel to help him rob a bank. The attorney general asks to meet with Pepito.

13.title: Episode #2.13
13.plot: Sara moves in with El Teca, who gives her a memorable welcome. Salvador sneaks off to visit a drug dealer and meets fellow customer Begoña.

14.title: Episode #2.14
14.plot: While searching for Salvador, Manuel runs into La Tuti and her attacker. Begoña introduces Salvador to a new drug. Sara sets up Quintanilla's capture.

15.title: Episode #2.15
15.plot: Pepito has a change of heart about his job offer. Quintanilla sees an opportunity to get back in the game. Sara asks to negotiate with the Chinese.

16.title: Episode #2.16
16.plot: Erick makes a strong impression on Briseida. Aracely questions Mario's intentions toward her. The DEA prepares to raid the meeting with the Chinese.

17.title: Episode #2.17
17.plot: After starting a three-way shootout, Breseida asks El Indio to hand Sara over to her. Aracely overhears Mario in a troubling conversation with Aldama.

18.title: Episode #2.18
18.plot: When El Teca catches Manuel coming to Sara's rescue, she makes a bold move to save his life. Sara forces El Teca to choose between her and El Indio.

19.title: Episode #2.19
19.plot: A heartbroken Manuel looks for a distraction. Josefina succumbs to Erick's advances. El Teca assigns Sara another test of loyalty.

20.title: Episode #2.20
20.plot: Salvador grabs a gun and goes to El Teca's ranch to get revenge. Mario seduces Aracely. Pepito confronts Begoña about her relationship with Salvador.

21.title: Episode #2.21
21.plot: Manuel seeks comfort in another woman's arms. Aldama and the music producer discuss their true interest in Aracely. El Teca reveals a family secret.

22.title: Episode #2.22
22.plot: Pepito follows Begoña to La Tuti's home, where Salvador is waiting for her. Sara faces an unthinkable task. Briseida makes Erick pay for his betrayal.

23.title: Episode #2.23
23.plot: El Indio is fired, but doesn't go quietly. When the Cali cartel's first smuggling job hits a snag, Erick takes extreme action to save the operation.

24.title: Episode #2.24
24.plot: Upon their return home, Aracely gets a big surprise from Mario. Quintanilla gives Salvador a gun and an ultimatum. Sara falls victim to Rosa's potion.

25.title: Episode #2.25
25.plot: El Indio follows Manuel and is shocked to see whom he meets up with. The attorney general tasks Pepito with identifying the suspects in the photo.

26.title: Episode #2.26
26.plot: Horacio has suspicions about Mario Casas' intentions. The DEA decides to arrest Marcelo and confront his boss. El Indio Amaro tortures Sara.

27.title: Episode #2.27
27.plot: The president chooses between his wife and Berta. Dóriga escapes from jail to rescue Sara. Aracely catches Miriam and Cristian in an intimate moment.

28.title: Episode #2.28
28.plot: Horacio confronts Mario alone. Berta gathers ammunition to use against the president. Sara goes to Manuel's home and is greeted by a surprise.

29.title: Episode #2.29
29.plot: Sara reveals to Manuel what happened to her at El Teca's ranch. El Indio calls El Teca's son. Begoña's father finds the gun under her bed.

30.title: Episode #2.30
30.plot: Sara tells her family the entire truth, but Quintanilla doesn't believe her. Sara and Briseida face off to the death.

31.title: Episode #2.31
31.plot: Erick shows Josefina what she's been missing. A stranger sweeps La Tuti off her feet. Álvaro corners Sara and Salvador at gunpoint.

32.title: Episode #2.32
32.plot: Sara walks in on a shocking scene. To get to Sara, Álvaro forms an alliance with La Tuti. Salvador starts to experience a diabetic complication.

33.title: Episode #2.33
33.plot: Sara makes a decision about her son. Erick refuses to accept his demotion and finds El Indio to avenge his mother's death. Mario tests his new drug.

34.title: Episode #2.34
34.plot: El Gallo and El Indio Amaro fight to the death. Manuel shoots Álvaro and El Teca's son saves Sara.

35.title: Episode #2.35
35.plot: The DEA targets Alicia again as a means of infiltration. La Tuti uses Salvador to lure Sara to her apartment. Horacio catches an intruder in his home.

36.title: Episode #2.36
36.plot: During a shootout, Álvaro makes a cowardly move. Quintanilla responds to Dóriga's request for help. Mario tells Sara he wants to make her an offer.

37.title: Episode #2.37
37.plot: The first lady reacts to Berta's exposé. Aracely cuts ties with Mario. Sara admits her son to rehab, and later meets with Mario to hear his proposal.

38.title: Episode #2.38
38.plot: A problem with one of his test patients threatens Mario's plans. Erick draws a line with Josefina. Berta plans to use Josefina to get to Sara.

39.title: Episode #2.39
39.plot: The Tijuana cartel suffers a big blow under Álvaro's leadership. Sara gets good news about Salvador. Briseida is shocked to see El Teca out in public.

40.title: Episode #2.40
40.plot: In a video, the drug trafficker tells Señora Acero that he'll make her pay. Caicedo promises that while he's alive, everything will be fine.

41.title: Episode #2.41
41.plot: Salvador's reunion with Begoña is not a happy one. El Teca forces Alfredo to be his double. Joaquín overhears Miriam discussing her doubts about him.

42.title: Episode #2.42
42.plot: Josefina makes a confession to Quintanilla. While El Indio trains Alfredo, Dóriga coaches Salvador. El Teca gains access to paramilitary weapons.

43.title: Episode #2.43
43.plot: Miriam begs Joaquín to stay. Berta introduces Josefina to Rosalinda's mom. La Tuti tells Manuel her news. Salvador steals a sample of Mario's drug.

44.title: Episode #2.44
44.plot: Berta forces Josefina to choose between her son and Sara. Javier overhears valuable intel via Alicia's bugged cellphone. Álvaro fires the bazooka.

45.title: Episode #2.45
45.plot: El Teca shows his double how to trap Señora Acero. Begoña escapes from the hospital. Horacio is shot at Aracely's show.

46.title: Episode #2.46
46.plot: Begoña begs Salvador to forgive her. Manuel tells Sara about La Tuti. Dóriga finds the transmitter on Alicia's phone. La Tuti makes demands of Manuel.

47.title: Episode #2.47
47.plot: Alfredo is put to the test. The attorney general follows a hunch. Alicia realizes Javier bugged her phone. Manuel asks Sara for a big personal favor.

48.title: Episode #2.48
48.plot: The attorney general confirms who Salvador's mother is. Berta serves as a surrogate for Sara. La Tuti moves in. Erick offers Josefina an alternative.

49.title: Episode #2.49
49.plot: The computer virus backfires on Pepito. El Tuti's attention-seeking behavior draws suspicion. Erick follows Josefina to her meeting with Berta.

50.title: Episode #2.50
50.plot: When Javier overhears Dóriga at the police raid, he swoops in to capture him. Begoña gives in to despair. La Tuti and Manuel get news from the doctor.

51.title: Episode #2.51
51.plot: Pepito turns the tables on the gunmen. When Manuel questions Sara's plans to rescue Dóriga, she explodes. Mario reveals a violent side to Aracely.

52.title: Episode #2.52
52.plot: Aracely threatens Mario so that he'll leave her alone. Sara launches an operation to save Dóriga.

53.title: Episode #2.53
53.plot: Miriam tries to bargain with the attorney general. Sara's team launches a plan to rescue Dóriga. Josefina calls Berta in order to trace her location.

54.title: Episode #2.54
54.plot: Salvador plots his route to Los Angeles via the tunnels, unaware that El Teca has his own plans to use them. Sara finds La Tuti's secret cellphone.

55.title: Episode #2.55
55.plot: Mario launches his drone distribution system. Sara and Berta face off during the hostage exchange. Salvador embarks on his journey to L.A.

56.title: Episode #2.56
56.plot: Dóriga confesses to Sara. La Tuti offers another man comfort. Salvador's health takes an untimely turn. Erick and Josefina reach a turning point.

57.title: Episode #2.57
57.plot: El Teca finds a new way to humiliate and punish Berta. Quintanilla reveals a family secret. Sara learns La Tuti told the attorney general about her.

58.title: Episode #2.58
58.plot: Sara reaches her limit with La Tuti, who may not be the only woman who's pregnant in the household. A hotel clerk recognizes a familiar face.

59.title: Episode #2.59
59.plot: Fearful of his next mission, Alfredo makes a run for it. Aldama gets what she wants. Two women receive test results. El Indio helps Berta escape.

60.title: Episode #2.60
60.plot: Manuel plots to help Salvador and Begoña return safely to Mexico. La Tuti calls Álvaro with news. El Teca ensures Alfredo never disobeys him again.

61.title: Episode #2.61
61.plot: Quintanilla and El Teca settle an old score. Mario's hospitalization reveals more than one secret. Berta tells Erick her news. Begoña gets a shock.

62.title: Episode #2.62
62.plot: Aracely leads a mission to steal the drug formula from Mario's lab. The cartel's lifestyle proves too much for Begoña. Álvaro brings a guest home.

63.title: Episode #2.63
63.plot: El Teca finds the bug on La Tuti's phone. A delivery rocks the Jalisco cartel to its core. Salvador tells Begoña the great lengths he'd go to for her.

64.title: Episode #2.64
64.plot: Begoña searches for a mental escape. El Teca tests La Tuti to see if she's an infiltrator. Stress and grief take a physical toll on Josefina.

65.title: Episode #2.65
65.plot: La Tuti is ambushed at her apartment. The attorney general follows his daughter's phone signal. Aracely learns the extent of Mario's crimes.

66.title: Episode #2.66
66.plot: Begoña makes a decision about her future. Aracely sets out to avenge Horacio's death. Erick sends a gift to El Teca. Sara interrogates La Tuti.

67.title: Episode #2.67
67.plot: La Tuti is forced to submit to a lie detector test. Begoña finds an ally sympathetic to her plight. Rosa gives El Teca a tip about El Indio.

68.title: Episode #2.68
68.plot: Refusing to let Begoña go, Salvador pulls a dangerous stunt. El Teca underestimates his men's loyalty to El Indio.

69.title: Episode #2.69
69.plot: Miriam comes to a decision about her son. Salvador gives Begoña a secret lifeline to her father. Sara receives a surprising request for a meeting.

70.title: Episode #2.70
70.plot: Salvador makes a bold proposal. Mario surfaces in Buenos Aires and calls Aracely. El Teca follows a tip on Pepito's whereabouts.

71.title: Episode #2.71
71.plot: El Teca takes steps to ensure Alfredo feels the same grief he does, but ends up creating a fierce foe in the process. Aracely visits Aldama in prison.

72.title: Episode #2.72
72.plot: Pepito warns the attorney general about Begoña's plans. In Buenos Aires, Mario hears a familiar voice singing. The mole leaks more info to El Teca.

73.title: Episode #2.73
73.plot: Dóriga leaves on a mysterious mission. El Teca's men lie in wait for Pepito. Aracely makes Mario pay. Hiding the gel, Alfredo surrenders to El Teca.

74.title: Episode #2.74
74.plot: Dóriga turns himself in to the DEA to protect Salvador. Señora Acero's son confesses that he betrayed Dóriga.

75.title: Episode #2.75
75.plot: Sara and her team track down El Teca, who keeps Alfredo close to confuse them. Dóriga helps Javier set up a trap to catch the mole.

imdb.plot outline: An innocent woman becomes haunted by the death of her husband to later learn that he secretly worked in the drug business. This woman, Sara, slowly begins her own drug trafficking business and becomes a woman she never expected to be. Sara fights endlessly to save her son from his severe diabetes and the opposing cartel, while having to do deal with a life of crime.
